<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-24">
        <span class="text-primary font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-4 block">The Heritage</span>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-display font-medium text-white mb-8 italic">Velocità</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-cream/80 font-display leading-relaxed italic border-y border-white/10 py-12">
            "We believe that driving is an art form, and the cars of the mid-20th century were its greatest masterpieces."
        </p>
    </div>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-center py-24">
        <div class="aspect-square rounded-full overflow-hidden chrome-border shadow-2xl group cursor-pointer">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541899481282-d53bffe3c35d?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" alt="Vintage Workshop" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-8">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-display text-white">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="text-cream/60 leading-relaxed font-light text-lg">
                Founded in 2018 in a small garage in Milan, Velocità was born from a simple desire: to make the most beautiful machines ever made accessible to those who truly appreciate them.
            </p>
            <p class="text-cream/60 leading-relaxed font-light text-lg">
                Today, our collection spans three continents. Each vehicle is sourced personally by our founders and maintained by master technicians who understand that these aren't just cars—they are time machines.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 border-t border-white/10">
                <div>
                    <div class="text-3xl font-display text-primary">42</div>
                    <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-cream/40">Icons in Collection</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="text-3xl font-display text-primary">12</div>
                    <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-cream/40">Curated Routes</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
